rture of the lens. Spot size is calculated with clipped effective beam and a penalty.","invalidLens":"Lens diameter and focal length must be greater than zero.","invalidHz":"Hz must be greater than zero.","expanderWarning":"The expanded beam exceeds a mirror or lens clear aperture, so clipping loss is included.","spotHeaderTitle":"CO2 source and measurement","readouts":"Readouts","brand":"Brand","model":"Model","excitation":"Excitation","defaultHz":"Default Hz","maxHz":"Max Hz","wavelength":"Wavelength","confidence":"Confidence","tubeLength":"Tube length","tubeDiameter":"Tube diameter","bestCurrent":"Best current","dataSource":"Data source","openSourceLink":"Open source link","lensLower":"lens","mirrorLower":"mirror","apertureSuffix":"aperture","opticalBaselineSuffix":"before finish, thermal, clipping, and alignment factors.","sourcePresetPlaceholder":"Select CO2 source preset","manualRatedWatt":"Manual rated watt","manualSourceBeam":"Manual source beam","manualM2":"Manual M²","manualSourceHint":"Use these fields when no source preset is selected.","selectedPower":"Selected power","minPower":"Min","maxPower":"Max","warningZone":"warning zone","percentUnit":"%","pulseGraphTitle":"Pulse / Hz graph","pulseGraphSub":"Pulse spacing and energy per pulse from selected watt and Hz.","pulseSelectedHz":"Selected Hz","pulseEnergyPerPulse":"Energy per pulse","hzZoomSlider":"Hz zoom selector","expandGraphPlus":"Open larger graph","zoomIn":"Zoom in","zoomOut":"Zoom out","panLeft":"Pan left","panRight":"Pan right","dragHzBar":"Drag the Hz bar to select frequency","lensPreviewTitle":"Lens shape preview","mirrorPreviewTitle":"Mirror finish preview","expanderGraphTitle":"Beam expander diagram","fullOpticalPathTitle":"Full optical path","stageSource":"CO2 source","stageCombiner":"Beam combiner","stageMirror1":"Mirror 1","stageMirror2":"Mirror 2","stageMirror3":"Mirror 3","stageLens":"Focus lens","stageSurface":"Material surface","energyAfterStage":"Energy after stage","beamDiameter":"